"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-sport-sport-olympics-paris-olympics-2024-day-one-schedule-highlights-team-gb-events-how-watch-today-b1173139.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sport|Olympics  TheParis Olympicsbegin today after a stunning opening ceremony on Friday night.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 324, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's the best of the action for day one,with the full schedule across the games available here.\", \"from\": 326, \"to\": 423, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"10am: Air rifle mixed team  The first gold medal of the Games is due to be won early Saturday morning at the Chateauroux Shooting Centre, one of 14 to be decided by the end of day one.\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 609, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At the same time, Britain's male gymnasts will be in action in qualifying, with Max Whitlock starting his campaign for an historic third successive pommel horse gold.\", \"from\": 610, \"to\": 776, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 628, \"end\": 635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9950703937469584, \"rank\": 0.00495402765887095, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 690, \"end\": 702, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Max Whitlock\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"1.30pm: Cycling time-trials  So much of Britain's Olympic success across the past two decades has come on two wheels, and there is hope for more of the same on the roads of Paris.\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 957, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 818, \"end\": 825, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9950703937469584, \"rank\": 0.00495402765887095, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 951, \"end\": 956, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1148829472981216e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the first time at the Games, men and women will compete over the same course and distance, starting and finishing by Pont Alexandre III.\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 1099, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1080, \"end\": 1098, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pont_Alexandre_III\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pont Alexandre III\", \"types\": [\"Q12280\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pont_Alexandre_III\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pont_Alexandre_III\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Anna Henderson, last year's European silver medalist, is up first in the women's event, but it is 20-year-old Josh Tarling who carries highest hopes of starting the medal rush in the men's event (from 3.32pm), having won world gold last year.\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1343, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1101, \"end\": 1115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Henderson\", \"score\": 0.9999958972009645, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anna Henderson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Henderson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Henderson\"}, {\"begin\": 1129, \"end\": 1153, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Figure_Skating_Championships\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"European silver medalist\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Figure_Skating_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Figure_Skating_Championships\"}, {\"begin\": 1211, \"end\": 1215, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Duggar\", \"score\": 0.8248386310769646, \"rank\": 0.21204818409371068, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Duggar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Duggar\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"6.45pm: Men's rugby sevens final  Having begun on Wednesday, two days before the opening ceremony, the men's sevens reaches its climax at the Stade de France, where locals hope national superstar Antoine Dupont can lead the hosts to victory.\", \"from\": 1345, \"to\": 1586, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1541, \"end\": 1555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antoine_Dupont\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Antoine Dupont\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13415036\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antoine_Dupont\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antoine_Dupont\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fiji, though, are the favourites to win a third straight gold.\", \"from\": 1587, \"to\": 1649, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1587, \"end\": 1591, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fiji_national_rugby_sevens_team\", \"score\": 0.9999561175365484, \"rank\": 4.031077949378255e-05, \"text\": \"Fiji\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fiji_national_rugby_sevens_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fiji_national_rugby_sevens_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"7.52pm: Women's 400m freestyle final  A lively first night of finals in the pool is headlined by what should be an epic three-way clash between reigning champion Ariarne Titmus, Olympic great Katie Ledecky and teenage upstart Summer McIntosh.\", \"from\": 1651, \"to\": 1893, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1813, \"end\": 1827, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariarne_Titmus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ariarne Titmus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariarne_Titmus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariarne_Titmus\"}, {\"begin\": 1843, \"end\": 1856, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katie Ledecky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\"}, {\"begin\": 1877, \"end\": 1892, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Summer_McIntosh\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Summer McIntosh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Summer_McIntosh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Summer_McIntosh\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"09.30:Shooting- 10m air rifle mixed team gold medal match  10.00:Diving- women's 3m synchronised springboard final  13.30:Cycling (road)- women's individual time trial  15.00:Judo- women's 48kg final and men's 60kg final  16.00:Skateboarding- men's street final  17.32:Cycling (road)- men's individual time trial  18.45:Rugby Sevens- men's gold medal match  19.42:Swimming- men's 400m freestyle final  19.52:Swimming- women's 400m freestyle final  20.30:Fencing- women's \\u00e9p\\u00e9e individual gold medal bout  20.34:Swimming- women's 4x100 freestyle relay final  20.44:Swimming- men's 4x100 freestyle relay final  20.55:Fencing- men's sabre individual gold medal bout  TV channel:The BBC has announced it will broadcast two live streams of the action from July 27 to August 11 - for the duration of the Games.\", \"from\": 1895, \"to\": 2698, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2573, \"end\": 2576, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9998036991979151, \"rank\": 0.0001963235661559265, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This will be on BBC One, BBC Two or a stream available by clicking the red button on Freeview or a smart TV.\", \"from\": 2699, \"to\": 2807, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2784, \"end\": 2792, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Freeview_(UK)\", \"score\": 0.9827493944847808, \"rank\": 0.01580453340061992, \"text\": \"Freeview\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Freeview_(UK)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Freeview_(UK)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is reduced coverage compared with previous years, however, when BBC broadcasted everything from archery to wrestling live on its website or channels.\", \"from\": 2809, \"to\": 2964, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2879, \"end\": 2882, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9998036991979151, \"rank\": 0.0001963235661559265, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, Discovery+ is the rights holder for Paris 2024 and is showing every moment across Eurosport channels in the UK from 7am-10.30pm every day.\", \"from\": 2965, \"to\": 3112, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3010, \"end\": 3020, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.066516276229867e-23, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 3082, \"end\": 3084, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9942184207440211, \"rank\": 0.005815199497488205, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Live stream:Fans can also catch the BBC coverage live online for free via the BBC Sport website and BBC iPlayer.\", \"from\": 3114, \"to\": 3226, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3150, \"end\": 3153, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9998036991979151, \"rank\": 0.0001963235661559265, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 3214, \"end\": 3217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9998036991979151, \"rank\": 0.0001963235661559265, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 3218, \"end\": 3225, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_iPlayer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"iPlayer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_iPlayer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_iPlayer\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Discovery+ app will be showing